### 회원가입
POST {{domain-gateway}}/api/v1/auth/register
Content-Type: {{json}}

{
    "loginId" : "vhkdrb521",
    "password" : "ghkddlsrb1!",
    "email" : "vhkdrb521@gmail.com",
    "phoneNumber" : "01049045402",
    "memberType" : "MEMBER"
}

### 로그인
# 응답: Access Token → Body, Refresh Token → HttpOnly Cookie(refresh_token) 자동 저장
POST {{domain-gateway}}/api/v1/auth/login
Content-Type: {{json}}

{
    "loginId" : "vhkdrb521",
    "password" : "ghkddlsrb1!"
}

> {%
    client.global.set("accessToken", response.body.data.accessToken);
%}

### 토큰 재발급
# Refresh Token은 쿠키에서 자동으로 전송됩니다 — Request Body 불필요
# IntelliJ HTTP Client가 Set-Cookie로 저장된 refresh_token을 자동으로 함께 전송합니다
POST {{domain-gateway}}/api/v1/auth/token/refresh

> {%
    client.global.set("accessToken", response.body.data.accessToken);
%}

### 이메일 인증
GET {{domain-gateway}}/api/v1/auth/verify-email?token={이메일로_받은_토큰}

### 로그아웃
# Redis의 Refresh Token 삭제 + Cookie 즉시 만료
POST {{domain-gateway}}/api/v1/auth/logout
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
